abstracts.cdata!:
This partial transcript, from the
            session of the Executive Directors of the International Bank
            for Reconstruction and Development (IBRD) and International
            Development Association (IDA) held on Thursday, June 10,
            1971 covers only the discussion on the Technical and
            Agricultural Education Credit for Senegal.
